|Example.Language=Spanish
|Example.Text=Sin embargo, no sólo en nuestro país, sino en muchos otros, la mayoría de la población sufre opresión económica no debido a su pereza, sino a las malas decisiones de gobernantes y líderes políticos que por su ambición y falta de sabiduría para manejar los asuntos financieros del país, llevan a la pobreza a sus gobernados y dan bienestar y ganancias económicas a unos cuantos.
|Example.Gloss=without restriction not only in our country but-also in many others the majority of the population suffers oppression economic not due to their sloth but-rather to the bad decisions of governors and leaders political that for their ambition and lack of wisdom to manage the issues financial of-the country bring to the poverty to their constituents and give well-being and profit economic to some few.
|Example.English translation=Nevertheless, not only in our country, but in many others, the majority of the population suffers economic oppression not due to laziness but to bad decisions on the part of governing officials and political leaders who, due to their ambition and lack of knowledge how to manage the financial issues of the country, bring their constituents to poverty and give wellbeing and economic profits to a few.
|Example.Provenance=http://www.elmanana.com.mx/notas.asp?id=96426
|Example.Comments=llevan a la pobreza a sus gobernados
