|Example.Gloss=we-notice without restriction that although the process of globalization constitutes a force dynamic that can benefit to all the countries in the practice its benefits refl distribute very unbalanced and we-express our determination of prevent and punish and mitigate the effects negative of globalization that carry to the poverty to-the underdevelopment and the exclusion social
